entries.journal_entry_description: Your career as a Hutt enforcer is going well. Osae, the boss on Yavin 4, wants you to intercept a cargo ship carrying Death Star salvage. Once you have done so you need to force the ship back to land at a remote spot on Yavin IV where Osae is waiting with a team.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Intercept and escort a cargo ship back to Yavin 4 before it can jump out of the system. Once you have done so return to Osae for your reward.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: The player has chosen to sell it to the Imperials.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: The player choses to sell the cargo to the Rebels.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: This is getting way to political. Tell Osae that you don't want to having anything more to do with her.
